company_description: INGINIOUS Clothing Co. is a womenswear brand that aims at targeting working women looking for breezy, comfortable yet chic styles that artfully combine work and play. The philosophy of our brand is to combine earthy simplicity and sophistication with just the right amount of flair and quirk, making workwear more reflective of the quintessential, urbane Indian woman.
commodity_description: Our products include shirts, trousers, dresses, etc that seamlessly combine the best of traditional Indian crafts with the comfort and charisma of modern western apparel. You will find naturally dyed, hand-spun, and handwoven cottons as well as linens crafted with minute attention to detail, tailored to perfection in the spirit of modern fashion. We aim to preempt and cater to the dynamic fashion needs of professional women with vibrant elegance and sustainability at the heart of it all.

company_description: I'm pleased to introduce myself as Prakash, Founder of Schopiq Automations, a start-up in the field of developing IoT-based technologies for Vending machines. We have successfully designed and developed a product, One-touch, multi-variant hot beverage vending machine called “BesTea,” intending to overcome the current limitations and develop tech-enabled tracking, billing, and inventory control for the vending machines.
commodity_description: The existing token-based vending machine requires a manual person to provide the tokens/coins. Our machines are Capable of running autonomously 24*7, Accepting UPI payments, and Reporting the machine data to the inventory, sales, and maintenance dashboard every minute. We have developed a dynamic reporting platform powered by IoT, Schopiq exclusively designed to monitor real-time sales and transaction. The hardware, software, dashboards, and automation tools were designed and developed in-house.
